title: ArcGIS Collection Status
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check reports errors and warnings encountered while the ArcGIS special
 agent collected data.

 The collection status service is a safety net for the special agent itself. It
 can show collection failures for Portal, federation, Server sites, service
 statistics, datastores, logs, licenses, and other collection steps.
item:
 This check has no item.
discovery:
 One service is discovered when collection status data is present.
